.Dd January 19, 2021
.Dt MTAGS 1
.Os
.
.Sh NAME
.Nm mtags
.Nd miscellaneous tags
.
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Op Fl a
.Op Fl f Ar tagsfile
.Ar
.
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
utility
makes a
.Pa tags
file for
.Xr ex 1
from the specified
.Xr make 1
and
.Xr mdoc 7
sources.
.
.Pp
The arguments are as follows:
.Bl -tag -width Ds
.It Fl a
Append to
.Pa tags
file.
.It Fl f Ar tagsfile
Place the tag descriptions
in a file called
.Ar tagsfile .
The default behaviour is
to place them in a file called
.Pa tags .
.El
.
.Pp
Files whose names are
.Pa Makefile
or end in
.Pa .mk
are assumed to be
.Xr make 1
files.
Files whose names end in
.Pa .[1-9]
are assumed to be
.Xr mdoc 7
files.
.
.Sh FILES
.Bl -tag -width Ds
.It Pa tags
default output tags file
.El
.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr ctags 1 ,
.Xr ex 1 ,
.Xr vi 1
